---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Co-Broke | MRT Real Estate"
  description="Política de co-brokerage de MRT Real Estate Puerto Rico. Trabajamos con todos los brokers licenciados para facilitar la venta de propiedades."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-navy-900 to-navy-800 py-16 px-4 -mt-20 pt-28">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white mb-4">
          Co-Broke <span class="text-gold-500">Policy</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg">
          Política de cooperación entre corredores de MRT Real Estate
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gold-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy-900">Cooperación entre Corredores</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500">MRT Real Estate — Lic. C-19882</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            MRT Real Estate (Lic. C-19882) mantiene una
            política abierta de cooperación con todos los corredores y agentes de bienes raíces
            debidamente licenciados en Puerto Rico.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-navy-900 mt-8">Términos de Co-Brokerage</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 ml-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Ofrecemos cooperación en todas nuestras propiedades listadas, salvo indicación contraria.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span>La comisión de co-broke será según lo acordado en el listado del MLS (Stellar MLS).</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span>El corredor cooperante debe estar debidamente licenciado por DACO y la Junta de Bienes Raíces de Puerto Rico.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Se requiere registro previo del cliente antes de la primera visita a la propiedad.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Todas las ofertas deben ser presentadas por escrito utilizando los formularios aprobados.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-navy-900 mt-8">Proceso</h3>
          <ol class="space-y-3 ml-4 list-decimal list-inside">
            <li><strong>Completar el formulario de Co-Broke</strong> que se encuentra a continuación.</li>
            <li>Contactar a MRT Real Estate para confirmar disponibilidad y términos de co-broke.</li>
            <li>Registrar al cliente comprador antes de coordinar visita.</li>
            <li>Coordinar showing a través de nuestro sistema de citas.</li>
            <li>Presentar ofertas formales con pre-cualificación del comprador.</li>
            <li>Cierre coordinado con el equipo legal y financiero.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Co-Broke Registration Form -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 mt-8" id="co-broke-form">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gold-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy-900">Formulario de Co-Broke</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500">Complete este formulario antes de agendar una cita de showing</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <form id="cobroke-form" class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Broker Info -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 text-lg mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">Información del Corredor</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Nombre Completo del Corredor *</label>
                <input type="text" name="broker_name" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Número de Licencia *</label>
                <input type="text" name="broker_license" required placeholder="Ej: C-12345" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Compañía / Brokerage *</label>
                <input type="text" name="broker_company" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Teléfono *</label>
                <input type="tel" name="broker_phone" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500" />
              </div>
              <div class="md:col-span-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Correo Electrónico *</label>
                <input type="email" name="broker_email" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Client Info -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 text-lg mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">Información del Cliente Comprador</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Nombre del Cliente *</label>
                <input type="text" name="client_name" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Teléfono del Cliente</label>
                <input type="tel" name="client_phone" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500" />
              </div>
              <div class="md:col-span-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">¿El cliente está pre-cualificado? *</label>
                <select name="prequalified" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500 bg-white">
                  <option value="">Seleccionar...</option>
                  <option value="si">Sí, está pre-cualificado</option>
                  <option value="en_proceso">En proceso de pre-cualificación</option>
                  <option value="no">No está pre-cualificado aún</option>
                  <option value="cash">Compra en efectivo (cash)</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Property Info -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 text-lg mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">Propiedad de Interés</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">MLS# o Dirección de la Propiedad *</label>
                <input type="text" name="property_id" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Fecha Preferida para Showing</label>
                <input type="date" name="preferred_date" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500" />
              </div>
              <div class="md:col-span-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Notas Adicionales</label>
                <textarea name="notes" rows="3" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:border-gold-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-500" placeholder="Cualquier información adicional relevante..."></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Agreement -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer">
              <input type="checkbox" name="agreement" required class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 text-gold-500 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-gold-500" />
              <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Certifico que soy un corredor o agente de bienes raíces debidamente licenciado por DACO y la Junta de Bienes Raíces de Puerto Rico. Acepto los términos de co-brokerage de MRT Real Estate y me comprometo a cumplir con la política de cooperación.
              </span>
            </label>
          </div>

          <!-- Submit -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <button type="submit" class="bg-gold-500 text-navy-900 px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-navy-900 hover:text-white transition-colors">
              Enviar Solicitud de Co-Broke
            </button>
          </div>

          <!-- Success/Error Messages -->
          <div id="cobroke-success" class="hidden bg-green-50 border border-green-200 text-green-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            Solicitud enviada exitosamente. Nos pondremos en contacto dentro de 24 horas hábiles.
          </div>
          <div id="cobroke-error" class="hidden bg-red-50 border border-red-200 text-red-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            Error al enviar. Por favor intente nuevamente o contáctenos directamente.
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact CTA -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 mt-8">
        <div class="bg-navy-900 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-white mb-3">¿Preguntas sobre Co-Broke?</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 mb-6">Contáctanos para discutir oportunidades de co-brokerage</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="tel:+17873261547" class="bg-gold-500 text-navy-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-white transition-colors">
              (787) 326-1547
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:marilyn@mrtrealestate.com" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-white hover:text-navy-900 transition-colors">
              marilyn@mrtrealestate.com
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    const GOOGLE_SCRIPT_URL = 'https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbye0qPFQnTL5cu5xV2T23g5n4w9CHjMgWWMhOPbLiJqcUtSmNpI1Qfeqkdyg3r_uyPw/exec';

    const form = document.getElementById('cobroke-form') as HTMLFormElement;
    const successMsg = document.getElementById('cobroke-success');
    const errorMsg = document.getElementById('cobroke-error');

    form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      successMsg?.classList.add('hidden');
      errorMsg?.classList.add('hidden');

      const submitBtn = form.querySelector('button[type="submit"]') as HTMLButtonElement;
      const originalText = submitBtn.textContent;
      submitBtn.disabled = true;
      submitBtn.textContent = 'Enviando...';

      const formData = new FormData(form);
      const data: Record<string, string> = {};
      formData.forEach((value, key) => {
        if (key !== 'agreement') data[key] = value.toString();
      });

      try {
        await fetch(GOOGLE_SCRIPT_URL === 'REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_GOOGLE_APPS_SCRIPT_URL'
          ? 'https://httpbin.org/post' : GOOGLE_SCRIPT_URL, {
          method: 'POST',
          mode: 'no-cors',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify({
            sheet: 'co-broke',
            timestamp: new Date().toLocaleString('es-PR', { timeZone: 'America/Puerto_Rico' }),
            ...data,
          }),
        });

        successMsg?.classList.remove('hidden');
        form.reset();
        successMsg?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
      } catch {
        errorMsg?.classList.remove('hidden');
      } finally {
        submitBtn.disabled = false;
        submitBtn.textContent = originalText;
      }
    });
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
